"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_terrorblade_reflection_lua"									"Reflection"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_terrorblade_reflection_lua_Description"						"Terrorblade brings forth an invulnerable dark reflection of all enemy heroes in a target area. Affected enemy heroes have movement and attack speeds slowed and attacked by their reflection. \nEnemy creeps are slowed and take physical damage equal to their base damage. Damage intervals are based on the creep's base attack time. Affects a maximum of %max_creep_affect% enemy creeps."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_terrorblade_reflection_lua_Lore"								"In the fractal prison of Foulfell, Terrorblade learned the truth of this old tale: you are your own worst enemy.Now it is a lesson he teaches others."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_terrorblade_reflection_lua_illusion_duration"					"REFLECTION DURATION:"
