"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_terrorblade_reflection_lua_attack_slow"						"ATTACK SPEED SLOW:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_terrorblade_reflection_lua_range"								"RADIUS:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_terrorblade_reflection_lua_Note0"								"Reflections are untargetable, invulnerable illusions, that will be destroyed if the slow debuff is removed."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_terrorblade_reflection_lua_Note1"								"Reflections can only attack their source."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_terrorblade_reflection_lua_ability_note"						"Enemy creeps are slowed and take physical damage equal to their base damage. Damage intervals are based on the creep's base attack time. Affects a maximum of %max_creep_affect% enemy creeps."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_terrorblade_reflection_lua_slow"							"REFLECTION"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_terrorblade_reflection_lua_slow_Description"				"Movement speed reduced by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_BONUS_PERCENTAGE%%%, attack speed reduced by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_ATTACKSPEED_BONUS_CONSTANT%."


"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_terrorblade_sunder_lua"					     "Sunder"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_terrorblade_sunder_lua_Description"		     "Severs the life from both Terrorblade and a target hero, exchanging a percentage of both units' current health. Somehealth points must remain."
